cvs: update tree -> cvs -d :pserver:release@cvs.liveops.com:/code co -r 'CC_2007-01-23-01_RELEASE' callcenterappeng 


cygwin: dd to USB drive at D:\ -> dd if=image.iso of=\\.\d: bs=4M


